<span class="line"><span style="color:#7F848E;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic">// 告诉RabbitMQ不要同时给消费端推送n条消息，一旦有n个消息还没ack，则该consumer将block掉，直到有ack；注意在自动应答下不生效</span></span>
